<HEADLINE> Entrepreneurs Discuss Shanghai's Development </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, November 3 (Xinhua) -- China's largest industrial
city has vowed to be on the cutting edge of international
competition surrounding information, biotechnology, financial and
high-technology sectors by the turn of the century.
</P>
