<HEADLINE> China Opposes US Interference In Tibetan Affairs </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, November 3 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese Government firmly
opposes the appointment of a "Special Coordinator of Tibetan
Affairs" by the US Government, Chinese Foreign Ministry Spokesman
Tang Guoqiang said today in response to reporters' questions.
</P>
