now agreed on practical ways we can learn from each other. This
agreement reflects the strengthening of Australia's links with
China, and the program of management development gives concrete
expression to the relationship," Newman said at the signing
ceremony.
</P>
<P>
She said the Australian Department of Social Security will help
China build on its capacity to develop broad social policy and to
move through a period of organizational and management change.
</P>
<P>
Chinese Vice-Minister of Labor Li said that through
implementing the program, Australia will be able to help China
produce a number of Chinese social security managerial
professionals, which will offer China a good opportunity to learn
the managerial and operational expertise suitable for a market
economy.
</P>
<P>
While restructuring its economy, China is developing its
much-needed social security system in order to ease the pressure
on its industries and provide direct social security assistance to
its workforce. 
