<HEADLINE> Zhanjiang Airport Expansion Completed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, November 3 (Xinhua) -- The Zhanjiang Airport
expansion project has been completed and the facility can now
handle large aircraft, including Boeing 757s.
</P>
<P>
