<HEADLINE> Highlights of Beijing Major Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, November 3 (Xinhua) -- Highlights of today's major
Beijing-based newspapers:
</P>
<P>
 "People's Daily"
</P>
<P>
-- This leading newspaper of the country continues to cover
