-- Premier Li Peng visited resettled people from Three Gorges
dam construction site during an inspection tour of the reservoir
which ended Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Li inspected the new towns and villages built for the former
residents of the reservoir area who were displaced because of the
construction.
</P>
