<HEADLINE> Backgrounder/Three Gorges: World's Largest Hydropower Plant (8) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Three Gorges Hydropower Station will be hooked up with
thermal power and hydroelectric grids in central and eastern
China, thus improving the economy and reliability of the electric
grids.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, China has mapped out state energy strategies by
transporting coal resources in northern China to the southern
regions and transmitting electricity generated from the western
parts to eastern localities in a bid to ease the energy shortage
in central and eastern China.  
</P>
